OL,6,FA train passenger fears receiving a
OL,7,Fcriminal record and being fined
OL,8,Fhundreds of pounds over a #1.90
OL,9,Funderpayment for rail travel.
OL,11,FSam Williamson said he is being
OL,12,Fprosecuted by Government-owned
OL,13,Foperator Northern because he used a
OL,14,Frailcard at the wrong time.
OL,16,FWriting on social media platform X,
OL,17,Fformerly known as Twitter, Mr
OL,18,FWilliamson stated that he used the
OL,19,FNorthern app to purchase a ticket from
OL,20,FBroadbottom, Greater Manchester, to
OL,21,Fcentral Manchester last month.
