OL,6,FThe ticket is named Anytime ` meaning
OL,7,Fthere are no restrictions on when the
OL,8,Fholder can travel ` but he bought it
OL,9,Fusing a railcard discount for
OL,10,Fpassengers aged 16-25.
OL,12,FMr Williamson wrote: "Once on the
OL,13,Ftrain, the conductor tells me my
OL,14,Fticket is invalid due to Railcard
OL,15,Frestrictions.
OL,17,F"I immediately offer to pay for a new
OL,18,Fticket, or even take a fixed penalty
OL,19,Ffare if needs be.
