OL,6,FOn Tuesday he received "a lovely
OL,7,Fletter from Northern Trains telling me
OL,8,Fabout how they wanted to prosecute
OL,9,Fme", he wrote.
OL,11,FHe added: "I've emailed the revenue
OL,12,Fprotection team with all the info I
OL,13,Fcan, so I hope this will work out OK.
OL,15,F"However, I'm understandably worried
OL,16,Fthat an innocent mistake over a
OL,17,Fconfusing and opaque rule ` that only
OL,18,Fsaved me #1.90! ` will lead to a
OL,19,Fpunishment of #100s and a criminal
OL,20,Frecord."
