OL,6,FA Northern spokesman said it would not
OL,7,Fbe appropriate to publicly comment on
OL,8,Fthe case.
OL,10,FHe went on: "As with all train
OL,11,Foperators across the UK, everyone has
OL,12,Fa duty to buy a valid ticket or obtain
OL,13,Fa promise to pay voucher before they
OL,14,Fboard the train and be able to present
OL,15,Fit to the conductor or revenue
OL,16,Fprotection officer during a ticket
OL,17,Finspection.
OL,19,F"The overwhelming majority of our
OL,20,Fcustomers ` upwards of 96% ` do just
OL,21,Fthat."
